div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-va-benzema-sap-doi-dau-nhau-o-serie-a-176-191165.html\">Ronaldo v\u00e0 Benzema s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau \u1edf Serie A?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/muon-oai-ronaldo-juventus-tinh-tai-hop-pogba-176-191121.html\">M\u01b0\u1ee3n oai Ronaldo, Juventus t\u00ednh t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/kevin-strootman-khong-ngai-doi-dau-ronaldo-tai-serie-a-176-191088.html\">Sao Roma kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Ronaldo c\u1ee7a Juventus</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1317","checkdouble":"191363"},{"date":"17:07 16/07","title":"Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Bayern Munich c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1eddi bi\u1ebft \u01a1n Guardiola","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/16/alaba-phat-bieu-ve-guardiola-va-thoi-gian-o-bayern.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>David Alaba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Guardiola, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng c\u00f3 3 n\u0103m l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c chung v\u1edbi anh t\u1ea1i Bayern Munich. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111a n\u0103ng n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1edd c\u00f3 Guardiola, anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p m\u1edbi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Guardiola \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi Alaba</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pep Guardiola t\u1eebng c\u00f3 qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Bayern Munich (n\u0103m 2013 t\u1edbi 2016). Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh t\u1edbi 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Bundesliga, 2 c\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c gia c\u00f9ng H\u00f9m x\u00e1m trong th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 ngai v\u00e0ng Champions League \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea3ng tr\u00e1nh th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Guardiola th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng Pep \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Bayern v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c khuy\u1ebft \u0111i danh hi\u1ec7u t\u1ea7m ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, David Alaba l\u1ea1i ngh\u0129 kh\u00e1c. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00c1o h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i th\u1ea7y c\u0169, ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh tin l\u00e0 \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Alaba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Guardiola, th\u1ea7y c\u0169 t\u1ea1i Bayern h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"David Alaba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Guardiola, th\u1ea7y c\u0169 t\u1ea1i Bayern h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/30/David-Alaba-phat-bieu-ve-HLV-Guardiola,-thay-cu-tai-Bayern-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Alaba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Guardiola v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 bi\u1ebft \u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft, Guardiola r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi t\u00f4i\u201d, Alaba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Guardiola. \u201c\u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p kh\u00e1c. Nh\u1edd \u00f4ng \u1ea5y, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 1 theo quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cGuardiola \u0111\u00e3 mang t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t phong c\u00e1ch m\u1edbi, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i Bayern. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng may m\u1eafn trong th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Alaba duoc Bayern dinh gia toi 80 trieu Euro\" title=\"David Alaba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bayern \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 t\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/8/4/Doi-hinh-xuat-sac-nhat-do-Robben-binh-chon-hinh-anh-5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Alaba tin th\u1ea7y c\u0169 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Guardiola s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAlaba kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi th\u1ea5y Guardiola ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Manchester City. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u00f4ng c\u00f9ng The Citizens gi\u00e0nh c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap danh hi\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0 c\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n. \u201cGuardiola \u0111ang l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c, gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf Anh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng\u201d, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u00c1o n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201cB\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1eafp t\u1edbi, Alaba s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i Guardiola khi Bayern so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Man City trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ng\u00e0y 29/7 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9. Sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho ra s\u00e2n \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro Cristiano Ronaldo chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 HLV Guardiola tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/pep-guardiola-the-khong-dinh-dang-gi-den-barcelona-nua-180-188217.html\">Pep Guardiola th\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng d\u00ednh d\u00e1ng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn Barcelona n\u1eefa</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/guardiola-phan-hoi-to-cao-cua-toure-172-188186.html\">Guardiola n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi b\u1ecb tr\u00f2 c\u0169 t\u1ed1 ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tro-cu-dua-ra-nhan-xet-kho-tin-ve-mourinho-va-guardiola-172-188015.html\">Tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t kh\u00f3 tin v\u1ec1 Mourinho v\u00e0 Guardiola</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/neymar-tha-thinh-man-city-pep-van-rat-tinh-don-172-187954.html\">Neymar \u201cth\u1ea3 th\u00ednh\u201d Man City, Pep v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t t\u1ec9nh \u0111\u00f2n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/yaya-toure-vs-pep-guardiola-nguoi-man-city-dung-ve-phia-ai-172-187848.html\">Yaya Toure vs Pep Guardiola: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda ai?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1316","checkdouble":"191364"},{"date":"16:37 16/07","title":"5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Hazard t\u1ea1i Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/31/5-cau-thu-co-the-thay-the-hazard-tai-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eb1ng anh mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi. Real nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn. V\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Hazard t\u1ea1i Chelsea.</h2><h2>Dries Mertens (Napoli)\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge n\u1ebfu Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge n\u1ebfu Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/3/10/5-cau-thu-co-the-cap-ben-Stamford-Bridge-neu-Hazard-roi-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mertens c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Napoli</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jorginho l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean theo ch\u00e2n HLV Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea. V\u1eady n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec qu\u00e1 ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu Mertens c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. Ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Serie A d\u01b0\u1edbi tay Sarri, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 46 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMertens ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u1edbi Hazard t\u1ea1i Naples. Anh c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Hazard tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 \u1edf World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 31, Mertens c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf ng\u1eafn h\u1ea1n cho Hazard. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn c\u1ee7a Mertens \u0111\u1ebfn h\u01a1i mu\u1ed9n khi anh ch\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t t\u1eeb n\u0103m 30 tu\u1ed5i. V\u1eady n\u00ean, Chelsea ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian n\u1eefa. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Chelsea khi \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Mertens ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 24.7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. V\u1edbi th\u1eddi gi\u00e1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 coi \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u1eddi v\u1edbi The Blues.</div>\r\n<h2>Hirving Lozano (PSV)\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Mexico tai World Cup 2018 dang co nhung don tan cong chop nhoang ma ban thang cua Lozano la vi du dien hinh.\" title=\"\u0110T Mexico t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1edbp nho\u00e1ng m\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Lozano l\u00e0 v\u00ed d\u1ee5 \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/Brazil-vs-Mexico-3-ly-do-de-tin-Mexico-se-tien-Brazil-ve-nuoc-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Lozano t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1ea5t \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn Lozano c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 t\u1ea1i Nga v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t sau khi World Cup kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. Anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 Lan khi ghi 17 b\u00e0n sau 29 tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLozano c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi Hazard. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i. Anh thu\u1eadn ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha ngo\u1eb7t v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y nguy hi\u1ec3m. Lozano l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nhanh nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Lozano m\u1edbi 22 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m x\u00fac khi \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 8 th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</div>\r\n<h2>Leon Bailey (Bayer Leverkusen)\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Leon Bailey\" title=\"Leon Bailey\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/26/chelsea-tang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-bundesliga-len-70-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Leon Bailey l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bailey l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. B\u1edfi sao tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y v\u1eabn \u0111ang ph\u00e2n v\u00e2n ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft n\u00ean thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia Anh hay B\u1ec9. Bailey m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 20 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea c\u0169ng c\u00f3 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Bailey trong th\u1eddi gian qua b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Man United. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bailey t\u1edbi Anh trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi. Bailey c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Sao tr\u1ebb 20 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y nhanh, tinh qu\u00e1i. \u0110\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 anh v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n th\u00eam v\u1ec1 kh\u00e2u d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<h2>Gareth Bale (Real Madrid)\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bale se quyet tam chung to minh khi Ronaldo ra di\" title=\"Bale s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh khi Ronaldo ra \u0111i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/chot-thoi-diem-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Bale c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u1ed7 cho Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho th\u1ea5y Bale d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Real Madrid sau khi kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Bernabeu. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo gi\u00fap Bale r\u1ed9ng c\u1eeda \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Bale. Anh \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 16 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i La Liga n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n 26 l\u1ea7n v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales c\u0169ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League khi ghi 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng si\u00eau \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Bale d\u00e0nh cho Chelsea. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4n kh\u00e9o, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e9p Real ph\u1ea3i nh\u1ea3 Bale \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Hazard h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<h2>Wilfried Zaha (Crystal Palace)\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Zaha cua Palace\" title=\"Zaha cua Palace\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/7/crystal-palace-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-man-city-va-tottenham-vu-zaha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Zaha gi\u00fap Palace tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Zaha ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 danh ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a anh \u1edf Crystal Palace l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd. &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng&rdquo; kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o trong s\u1ed1 9 tr\u1eadn m\u00e0 Zaha v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap Palace tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nZaha c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn Chelsea th\u1ea5y h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. Anh c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t, t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i. Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, m\u1ed9t c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t. V\u00e0 NHM ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd Zaha l\u00e0m n\u00ean nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nhay-vao-cuoc-dua-gianh-pogba-serbia-172-191339.html\">Chelsea nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Pogba Serbia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-sap-chao-don-4-tan-binh-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-191319.html\">Chelsea s\u1eafp ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n 4 t\u00e2n binh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1315","checkdouble":"191365"},{"date":"17:48 16/07","title":"Sao tr\u1ebb Liverpool ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/grujic-roi-liverpool-sang-cardiff.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Marko Grujic r\u1eddi Liverpool t\u1edbi Cardiff d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Wales v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 l\u00ean ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Premier League.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Grujic g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i Cardiff</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMarko Grujic t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Serbia v\u00e0 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Anh t\u1eebng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i U20 Serbia v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2015 v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt t\u1ea1i CLB Sao \u0111\u1ecf Belgrade m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2015/16.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQua \u0111\u00f3, Grujic l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Sau c\u00f9ng, nh\u01b0 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng Real Madrid hay Barcelona \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi Liverpool \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2016. Ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi nay, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 chen ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh The Kop.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Grujic r\u1eddi Liverpool t\u1edbi Cardiff d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Grujic r\u1eddi Liverpool t\u1edbi Cardiff d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/Grujic-roi-Liverpool-toi-Cardiff-duoi-dang-cho-muon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Grujic ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i Cardiff</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018, Grujic r\u1eddi Liverpool t\u1edbi Cardiff d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, anh g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi HLV Neil Warnock v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i x\u00f4ng x\u00e1o v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u1ecdi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn. Grujic c\u00f9ng Cardiff gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp l\u00ean ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jurgen Klopp r\u1ea5t ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Grujic. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia v\u1edbi th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng sung m\u00e3n r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch pressing v\u1edbi c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 cao m\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Grujic cua Liverpool\" title=\"Grujic c\u1ee7a Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/grujic-roi-liverpool-sang-cardiff.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Grujic r\u1eddi Liverpool t\u1edbi Cardiff d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n l\u1ea7n 2</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u Klopp kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho Grujic v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Liverpool m\u1edbi t\u1eadu th\u00eam nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m nh\u01b0 Naby Keita hay Fabinho v\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho ch\u00e0ng trai 22 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u00edt \u1ecfi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd cho Grujic ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Cardiff d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBan \u0111\u1ea7u, Grujic c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch c\u00f9ng Liverpool sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh ph\u1ea3i h\u1ee7y k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 t\u1edbi Cardiff ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i gia nh\u1eadp CLB x\u1ee9 Wales.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-noi-gi-ve-tan-binh-shaqiri-cua-liverpool-172-191149.html\">HLV Klopp n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Shaqiri c\u1ee7a Liverpool?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-xherdan-shaqiri-172-191137.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Xherdan Shaqiri</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/psg-va-juventus-muon-mua-brewster-sao-tre-liverpool-172-191041.html\">PSG v\u00e0 Juventus nh\u0103m nhe th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-thua-nuoc-duc-tha-cau-vu-ronaldo-toi-juventus-172-191026.html\">Liverpool th\u1eeba n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ee5c th\u1ea3 c\u00e2u v\u1ee5 Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sadio-mane-noi-gi-khi-duoc-real-madrid-quan-tam-172-190673.html\">Sadio Mane n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1314","checkdouble":"191368"},{"date":"17:27 16/07","title":"Qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng! Kante \"ng\u1ed1 t\u00e0u\" ng\u1ea1i \u0111i h\u1ecfi xin, nh\u1edd b\u1ea1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u1ed9 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1ng \u1ea3o","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/16/qua-de-thuong-kante-ngo-tau-ngai-di-hoi-xin-nho-ban-muon-ho-cup-vang-de-song-ao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Chelsea ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</h2><p><em><strong>Kante hi\u1ec1n l\u00e0nh d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng qu\u00e1, b\u1ecb c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p qu\u00e2y l\u1ea1i tr\u00eau gh\u1eb9o m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft ng\u1ed3i c\u01b0\u1eddi! (ngu\u1ed3n: Troll B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1)</strong></em></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/16/Troll-Bong-Da---Kante-hien-qua-a-ai-cung-treu.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng hi\u1ebfm hoi trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/cuoc-dua-qbv-the-gioi-2018-dien-ten-luka-modric-duoc-chua-421-191054.html\" target=\"_blank\">Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng Luka Modric</span>, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed s\u1edbm b\u1ecb thay ra khi th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ed9t gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3, kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a N\u2019Golo Kante tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea5p CLB g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 Leicester tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black\">Ch\u1eb3ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bu\u00f4ng l\u1eddi n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 tr\u00e1ch c\u1ee9, ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Kante h\u1ebft, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sau khi hay bi\u1ebft th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng y\u00eau qu\u00fd, tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng anh h\u01a1n. Chuy\u1ec7n ng\u00f4i sao Chelsea m\u00e1u l\u1eeda tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf nh\u01b0ng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c hi\u1ec1n l\u00e0nh, d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng pitch th\u00ec ai c\u0169ng r\u00f5, nh\u01b0ng ng\u1ea1i ng\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng d\u00e1m h\u1ecfi xin c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i cho c\u1ea7m c\u00fap ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m th\u00ec \u0111\u00fang th\u1eadt\u2026 s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t tr\u00ean \u0111\u1eddi.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng! Kante ng\u1ed1 t\u00e0u ng\u1ea1i \u0111i h\u1ecfi xin, nh\u1edd b\u1ea1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u1ed9 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1ng \u1ea3o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng! Kante ng\u1ed1 t\u00e0u ng\u1ea1i \u0111i h\u1ecfi xin, nh\u1edd b\u1ea1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u1ed9 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1ng \u1ea3o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/171529-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u1ea5m \u1ea3nh duy nh\u1ea5t ch\u1ee9ng minh Kante v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black\">Tr\u00f4ng sang \u201cth\u00e1nh \u0103n h\u00f4i\u201d Benjamin Mendy s\u1ed1ng \u1ea3o ra sao v\u1edbi c\u00fap v\u00e0ng, hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Olivier Giroud tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i m\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u201cch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7\u201d tuy\u1ec7t hay \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean b\u1ee5c nh\u1eadn c\u00fap, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u00e0ng ph\u1ea3i bu\u1ed3n c\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00e2n ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u1ed1 t\u00e0u c\u1ee7a thanh ni\u00ean Kante, d\u00f9 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 m\u00e0 anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black\">Kante c\u0169ng th\u00edch s\u1ed1ng \u1ea3o l\u1eafm ch\u1ee9, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i ng\u1ea1i ph\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1m l\u00e0m phi\u1ec1n l\u0169 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00f4 t\u00e2m kia \u0111ang thi nhau truy\u1ec1n tay c\u00fap v\u00e0ng, ch\u1ec9 d\u00e1m \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u1ea1nh b\u00ean b\u1ebdn l\u1ebdn v\u00e0\u2026 nhe r\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddi. May m\u1eafn thay c\u00f2n c\u00f3 \u00f4ng b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n Steve N\u2019Zonzi t\u00e2m l\u00fd, ch\u1ea1y \u0111i ch\u1ea1y l\u1ea1i y\u00eau c\u1ea7u m\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ee9a kia cho Kante m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00fap l\u00e0m p\u00f4 \u1ea3nh k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m cho \u0111\u1ee1 t\u1ee7i th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ed9i nghi\u1ec7p.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u1ebfu Lionel Messi c\u00f3 m\u1ea3y may quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed n\u00e1n l\u1ea1i xem n\u1ed1t m\u00e0n trao c\u00fap, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1ee9c b\u1ee5ng th\u1ea7m ngh\u0129: <em style=\"\"><b style=\"color: black;\">\u201cM\u00e0y ng\u1ea1i b\u00e1m theo tao v\u00e0 ng\u1ea1i t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y th\u00ec t\u1ed1t bi\u1ebft m\u1ea5y nh\u1ec9!\u201d</b><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Kante nh\u1edd N'Zonzi m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u1ed9 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng cho m\u00e0 s\u1ed1ng \u1ea3o!<br>\r\n</b></em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/16/Facebook.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng! Kante ng\u1ed1 t\u00e0u ng\u1ea1i \u0111i h\u1ecfi xin, nh\u1edd b\u1ea1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u1ed9 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1ng \u1ea3o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng! Kante ng\u1ed1 t\u00e0u ng\u1ea1i \u0111i h\u1ecfi xin, nh\u1edd b\u1ea1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u1ed9 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1ng \u1ea3o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/Qua-de-thuong!-Kante-ngo-tau-ngai-di-hoi-xin,-nho-ban-muon-ho-cup-vang-de-song-ao-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng b\u1ecb b\u1ecf r\u01a1i v\u00e0 to\u00e9t mi\u1ec7ng c\u01b0\u1eddi cam ch\u1ecbu khi nh\u1eadn c\u00fap t\u1eeb b\u00e9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng! Kante ng\u1ed1 t\u00e0u ng\u1ea1i \u0111i h\u1ecfi xin, nh\u1edd b\u1ea1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u1ed9 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1ng \u1ea3o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng! Kante ng\u1ed1 t\u00e0u ng\u1ea1i \u0111i h\u1ecfi xin, nh\u1edd b\u1ea1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u1ed9 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1ng \u1ea3o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/Qua-de-thuong!-Kante-ngo-tau-ngai-di-hoi-xin,-nho-ban-muon-ho-cup-vang-de-song-ao-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kante v\u00e0 n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7y r\u0103ng l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ef1c tr\u00ean m\u00f4i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng! Kante ng\u1ed1 t\u00e0u ng\u1ea1i \u0111i h\u1ecfi xin, nh\u1edd b\u1ea1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u1ed9 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1ng \u1ea3o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng! Kante ng\u1ed1 t\u00e0u ng\u1ea1i \u0111i h\u1ecfi xin, nh\u1edd b\u1ea1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u1ed9 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1ng \u1ea3o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/Qua-de-thuong!-Kante-ngo-tau-ngai-di-hoi-xin,-nho-ban-muon-ho-cup-vang-de-song-ao-hinh-anh-4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>50 s\u1eafc th\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Kante</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng! Kante ng\u1ed1 t\u00e0u ng\u1ea1i \u0111i h\u1ecfi xin, nh\u1edd b\u1ea1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u1ed9 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1ng \u1ea3o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng! Kante ng\u1ed1 t\u00e0u ng\u1ea1i \u0111i h\u1ecfi xin, nh\u1edd b\u1ea1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u1ed9 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1ng \u1ea3o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/171541-5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kante - Thanh ni\u00ean hi\u1ec1n l\u00e0nh, d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng, ch\u00e2n ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i... ng\u1ed1 t\u00e0u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c!</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-ranh-gioi-giua-binh-thuong-va-bat-thuong-421-191341.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/144833-1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-ranh-gioi-giua-binh-thuong-va-bat-thuong-421-191341.html\">Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018: Ranh gi\u1edbi gi\u1eefa b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng</span><br>\r\nNg\u00e0y h\u1ea1 m\u00e0n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, th\u1ebf r\u1ed3i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang ta \u0111i h\u1ebft t\u1eeb b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hau-chung-ket-world-cup-2018-khi-nguoi-thang-va-ke-thua-deu-do-ra-duong-465-191335.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/hau-chung-ket-world-cup-2018-khi-nguoi-thang-va-ke-thua-deu-do-ra-duong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hau-chung-ket-world-cup-2018-khi-nguoi-thang-va-ke-thua-deu-do-ra-duong-465-191335.html\">H\u1eadu chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: Khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eafng v\u00e0 k\u1ebb thua \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 qua v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a mang t\u00ednh bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 th\u1eafng hay thua, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t qu\u1ed1c gia...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1313","checkdouble":"191369"},{"date":"09:50 16/07","title":"Mourinho mong m\u1ecfi sao s\u00e1ng Croatia s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/mourinho-len-tieng-hy-vong-sao-sang-croatia-se-gia-nhap-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Ivan Perisic trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Croatia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>HLV Mourinho mu\u1ed1n M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9\u00a0<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Perisic</span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU HLV Mourinho mu\u1ed1n MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ivan Perisic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU HLV Mourinho mu\u1ed1n MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ivan Perisic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-HLV-Mourinho-muon-MU-chieu-mo-Ivan-Perisic-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Perisic l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 HLV Mourinho mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Perisic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t VCK World Cup 2018 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Croatia. Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup. \u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 n\u00e0y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 anh t\u1eeb Inter Milan. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y trong ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh Russia Today, HLV Mourinho v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ivan Perisic, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 anh v\u1eeba gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Ivan Perisic? Anh \u1ea5y \u0111i t\u1eeb Croatia \u0111\u1ebfn Borussia, Dortmund, Wolfburg r\u1ed3i b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 Inter Milan.\u00a0T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea1i sao Perisic l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn Man United khi t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n anh \u1ea5y\",\u00a0HLV Mourinho chia s\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, Mourinho c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfc l\u1eddi khen n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Perisic: \u201cPerisic l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t th\u1ea3y. Nhanh nh\u1eb9n v\u00e0 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t quen thu\u1ed9c m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta hay n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng bi\u00ean gi\u1ecfi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng Perisic th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00f3. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i. V\u00f4 c\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. V\u00e0 Perisic c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn n\u1eefa. C\u00e1ch c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e8 r\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng cho Mario Mandzukic ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Inter. Tuy nhi\u00ean sau World Cup 2018, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y cho Perisic.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh \u0111\u01b0a tin, ph\u00eda M.U mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng (50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) c\u1ee7a 1 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia Matteo Darmian cho Inter \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Perisic ngay trong H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/roy-keane-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-that-bai-cua-dt-anh-421-191201.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/roy-keane-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-that-bai-cua-dt-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/roy-keane-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-that-bai-cua-dt-anh-421-191201.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e9p v\u1ebf v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 trong tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng Ba tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U Roy Keane \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/dai-dien-cua-perisic-co-mat-tai-manchester-172-191192.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/dai-dien-cua-perisic-co-mat-tai-manchester.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/dai-dien-cua-perisic-co-mat-tai-manchester-172-191192.html\">Th\u00eam b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng cho th\u1ea5y M.U s\u1eafp c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u0110T Croatia</span><br>\r\nB\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Perisic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Manchester \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi BL\u0110 M.U.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/mu-day-manh-qua-trinh-mua-gareth-bale-180-191077.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/1/gareth-bale-duoc-khuyen-bo-real-ve-voi-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/mu-day-manh-qua-trinh-mua-gareth-bale-180-191077.html\">M.U \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u201csao b\u1ef1\u201d Real</span><br>\r\nSau khi m\u1ea5t \u0111i Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0o tay Juventus, Real Madrid l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi n\u1ed7i lo m\u1ea5t th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao n\u1eefa. Th\u00f4ng tin MU \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh mua Gareth...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1312","checkdouble":"191324"},{"date":"10:13 16/07","title":"Ibrahimovic khen Pogba sau danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/ibrahimovic-khen-pogba-sau-danh-hieu-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Zlatan Ibrahimovic \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh cho Pogba sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi Croatia \u0111\u00eam qua.</h2><h2>Ibra khen ng\u1ee3i Pogba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pogba \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p trong hi\u1ec7p hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Croatia. V\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t d\u1eadp t\u1eaft tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Vatreni.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 Ibrahimovic \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khen ng\u1ee3i m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Pogba tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Balkan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ibrahimovic khen Pogba sau danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ibrahimovic khen Pogba sau danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/ibrahimovic-khen-pogba-sau-danh-hieu-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Ibrahimovic khen Pogba tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00f3i thay t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3\u201d, Ibrahimovic chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Twitter v\u00e0 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i t\u1ea5m \u1ea3nh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang \u00f4m chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng World Cup.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nPogba v\u00e0 Ibrahimovic l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2016/17. Nh\u1edd hai ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y, Man \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi 3 danh hi\u1ec7u. Nh\u01b0ng sau s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Lukaku, Ibrahimovic \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn LA Galaxy v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u, Pogba ch\u01a1i l\u0103n x\u1ea3 v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 h\u00f4m qua l\u00e0 Croatia \u1edf hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, Pogba t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 4 l\u1ea7n, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 Kante. S\u1ea3i ch\u00e2n d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Pogba khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00e0 khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Lloris nh\u1edd v\u1eady c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o an to\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n trong kh\u00e2u t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, Pogba c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng. Anh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng n\u00e2ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 3-1 v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p ch\u01a1i th\u1ea3nh th\u1eddi h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/cdv-phap-phan-khich-va-qua-khich-an-mung-doi-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-461-191328.html\">C\u0110V Ph\u00e1p ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch v\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nong-tien-ve-pogba-hat-its-coming-home-che-nhao-nuoc-anh-421-191310.html\">N\u00d3NG: Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pogba h\u00e1t It's coming home ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1311","checkdouble":"191326"},{"date":"09:39 16/07","title":"C\u0110V Ph\u00e1p ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch v\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/cdv-phap-phan-khich-va-qua-khich-an-mung-doi-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.</h2><h2>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi chu\u1ed1i 7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a CLB SLNA</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb ch\u1ed7 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng, CLB SLNA \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd khi gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 21 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong 7 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1p \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 4 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n k\u00e9m t\u1ed1p 3 \u0111\u00fang 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng b\u1ecb s\u1ed1c khi SLNA to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 7 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng b\u1ecb s\u1ed1c khi SLNA to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 7 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/26/HLV-Nguyen-Duc-Thang-bi-soc-khi-SLNA-toan-thang-7-tran-lien-tiep-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 SLNA</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 NHM h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Ngay c\u1ea3 HLV SLNA, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n t\u1eebng su\u00fdt t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c SLNA cho hay: \u201cT\u00f4i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch 7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a SLNA. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng t\u00f4i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1eeba qua. Ti\u00eau ch\u00ed c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh, ni\u1ec1m vui chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng nhau s\u1ebb chia\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan trong ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. \u00d4ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201cTrong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, sai s\u00f3t hay c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i lu\u00f4n x\u1ea3y ra. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung, lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m\u201d. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, SLNA s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm l\u00e0 HAGL. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n, k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb \u0111ang l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/slna-vs-quang-nam-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191249.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/slna-vs-quang-nam-vong-19-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/slna-vs-quang-nam-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191249.html\">SLNA 2-1 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam (KT): Thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ee9 7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Th\u1eafng v\u00e0 Olaha, SLNA \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00fa l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam FC, qua \u0111\u00f3 n\u00e2ng chu\u1ed7i to\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 7.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/giup-slna-co-3-diem-phan-van-duc-nhan-duoc-loi-khen-co-canh-cua-doi-thu-168-189826.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/giup-slna-co-3-diem-phan-van-duc-nhan-duoc-loi-khen-co-canh-cua-doi-thu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/giup-slna-co-3-diem-phan-van-duc-nhan-duoc-loi-khen-co-canh-cua-doi-thu-168-189826.html\">Gi\u00fap SLNA c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho t\u00e0i n\u0103ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1310","checkdouble":"191328"},{"date":"10:04 16/07","title":"C\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t Paris \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 C\u0110V qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch sau khi Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/canh-sat-paris-dung-do-cdv-qua-khich-sau-khi-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1eeb m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng sau khi \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ph\u00e1 ho\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ed1ng b\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t Paris ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea5n \u00e1p.</h2><div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-croatia-461-191274.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/croatia-nhung-nguoi-viet-nen-lich-su.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-croatia-461-191274.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia (Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nCroatia kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup khi thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u1edf chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0nh nh\u00ecn Les Bleus l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t Paris \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 C\u0110V qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 4-2 trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, \u0110T Ph\u00e1p tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean Ph\u00e1p tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf s\u00e2n Luzhniki \u0103n m\u1eebng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 tr\u00ean to\u00e0n n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0103n m\u1eebng l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai Les Bleus \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t Paris \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 C\u0110V qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch sau khi Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t Paris \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 C\u0110V qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch sau khi Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/canh-sat-paris-dung-do-cdv-qua-khich-sau-khi-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t Paris \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 C\u0110V qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch sau khi Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e0ng ngh\u00ecn ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 Champs-Elysees \u0111\u1ec3 \u0103n m\u1eebng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Ph\u00e1p tr\u1edf n\u00ean k\u00e9m vui khi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 C\u0110V qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng g\u00e2y r\u1ed1i. H\u1ecd n\u00e9m \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0o c\u00e1c c\u1eeda k\u00ednh quanh \u0111\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 Champs-Elysees.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Sky Sports, kho\u1ea3ng 30 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111eo m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 tr\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 lao v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u01b0\u1edbp r\u01b0\u1ee3u. C\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t ch\u1ed1ng b\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng Paris bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i t\u00e1n nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch b\u1eb1ng s\u00fang n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 h\u01a1i cay. \u0110\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 danh ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Paris ch\u1ec9 d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 v\u1ebb b\u00ecnh y\u00ean v\u00e0o 11h30 \u0111\u00eam (theo gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ed5 ra \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u n\u01a1i<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Paris, nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 l\u1edbn kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng r\u01a1i v\u00e0o c\u1ea3nh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 khi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 C\u0110V qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u g\u00e2y r\u1ed1i. Theo c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Lyon x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn, c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t v\u00e0 C\u0110V qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 khi g\u1ea7n 100 thanh thi\u1ebfu ni\u00ean c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh leo l\u00ean m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc xe c\u1ee9u h\u1ecfa.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ea1n kh\u00ed cay \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i t\u00e1n nh\u1eefng thanh ni\u00ean k\u00edch \u0111\u1ed9ng khi h\u1ecd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed1t l\u1eeda v\u00e0 n\u00e9m c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 v\u1eadt v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng an ninh. \u1ede Marseille, 10 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb b\u1eaft v\u00e0 2 c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t b\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 C\u0110V qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/16/French-cops-deploy-tear-gas-&-water-cannons-to-contain-fan-frenzy-after-World-Cup-win-()---RT.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/16/Police-and-football-fans-clash-in-Paris-after-France\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/cdv-phap-phan-khich-va-qua-khich-an-mung-doi-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-461-191328.html\">C\u0110V Ph\u00e1p ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch v\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tuyen-phap-quay-tung-phong-hop-bao-sau-chuc-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-461-191325.html\">Tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p qu\u1eady t\u01b0ng ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-nhan-gui-real-madrid-sau-khi-vo-dich-world-cup-421-191317.html\">Mbappe nh\u1eafn g\u1eedi Real Madrid sau khi v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/griezmann-nghi-sao-khi-chau-phi-vo-dich-world-cup-khong-phai-phap-421-191315.html\">Griezmann ngh\u0129 sao khi Ch\u00e2u Phi v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nong-tien-ve-pogba-hat-its-coming-home-che-nhao-nuoc-anh-421-191310.html\">N\u00d3NG: Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pogba h\u00e1t It's coming home ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/gianh-chuc-vo-dich-varane-di-vao-lich-su-421-191308.html\">Gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Varane s\u00e1nh ngang Beckenbauer v\u00e0 Carlos</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1309","checkdouble":"191330"},{"date":"10:08 16/07","title":"\u0110\u00e1nh r\u01a1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HLV Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/20/danh-roi-chien-thang-truoc-clb-ha-noi-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 'k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u' \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 19 V-League.</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 15/7, CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 t\u1edbi Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 g\u1eb7p CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed cho t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC l\u00e0 c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn l\u00e0 v\u1eady song c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn khi ghi t\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Diogo v\u00e0 Th\u1ebf V\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ecbp g\u1ee1 l\u1ea1i 3 b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ebd m\u1eb7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng hai \u0111\u1ed9i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Van Sy\" title=\"HLV V\u0103n S\u1ef9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/danh-roi-chien-thang-truoc-clb-ha-noi-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc khi Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh b\u1ecb H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 3-3</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 n\u00f3i: &ldquo;C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i qu\u00e1 non n\u1edbt, n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi nh\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i th\u00ec m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 sao 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t r\u1ed3i, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh b\u1ecb cu\u1ed1n theo nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u00e2u b\u00f3ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00eam cho c\u00e1c em. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 thua. G\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, t\u00e2m l\u00fd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00e0ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i s\u1ee3 s\u1ec7t k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi thua tr\u1eadn&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng S\u1ef9 c\u0169ng g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eb7n l\u1ed9i m\u01b0a gi\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng con c\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 t\u1eeb kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 v\u00e0 C\u0110V \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. H\u00f4m nay v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 1, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, v\u00ec b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00e0 l\u00e0 v\u00ec t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3&rdquo;, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh FC n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i gi\u00fap Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng khi h\u01a1n S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/ha-noi-vs-nam-dinh-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191252.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/ha-noi-vs-nam-dinh-vong-19-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/ha-noi-vs-nam-dinh-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191252.html\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 3-3 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh (KT): D\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 3-0, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00f2ng 19 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/cdv-nam-dinh-doi-mua-dot-phao-ngay-tai-hang-day-291-191271.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/cdv-nam-dinh-doi-mua-dot-phao-ngay-tai-hang-day.JPEG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/vleague/cdv-nam-dinh-doi-mua-dot-phao-ngay-tai-hang-day-291-191271.html\">C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i m\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng ngay t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby</span><br>\r\nC\u01a1n m\u01b0a t\u1ea7m t\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m v\u01a1i \u0111i s\u1ef1 cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 19 V-League, C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i, trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1308","checkdouble":"191331"},{"date":"10:26 16/07","title":"HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng b\u1ecb s\u1ed1c khi SLNA to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 7 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/slna-toan-thang-7-tran-lien-tiep-hlv-nguyen-duc-thang-bi-soc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.</h2><h2>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi chu\u1ed1i 7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a CLB SLNA</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb ch\u1ed7 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng, CLB SLNA \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd khi gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 21 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong 7 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1p \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 4 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n k\u00e9m t\u1ed1p 3 \u0111\u00fang 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng b\u1ecb s\u1ed1c khi SLNA to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 7 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng b\u1ecb s\u1ed1c khi SLNA to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 7 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/26/HLV-Nguyen-Duc-Thang-bi-soc-khi-SLNA-toan-thang-7-tran-lien-tiep-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 SLNA</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 NHM h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Ngay c\u1ea3 HLV SLNA, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n t\u1eebng su\u00fdt t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c SLNA cho hay: \u201cT\u00f4i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch 7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a SLNA. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng t\u00f4i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1eeba qua. Ti\u00eau ch\u00ed c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh, ni\u1ec1m vui chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng nhau s\u1ebb chia\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan trong ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. \u00d4ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201cTrong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, sai s\u00f3t hay c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i lu\u00f4n x\u1ea3y ra. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung, lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m\u201d. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, SLNA s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm l\u00e0 HAGL. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n, k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb \u0111ang l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/slna-vs-quang-nam-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191249.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/slna-vs-quang-nam-vong-19-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/slna-vs-quang-nam-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191249.html\">SLNA 2-1 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam (KT): Thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ee9 7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Th\u1eafng v\u00e0 Olaha, SLNA \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00fa l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam FC, qua \u0111\u00f3 n\u00e2ng chu\u1ed7i to\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 7.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/giup-slna-co-3-diem-phan-van-duc-nhan-duoc-loi-khen-co-canh-cua-doi-thu-168-189826.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/giup-slna-co-3-diem-phan-van-duc-nhan-duoc-loi-khen-co-canh-cua-doi-thu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/giup-slna-co-3-diem-phan-van-duc-nhan-duoc-loi-khen-co-canh-cua-doi-thu-168-189826.html\">Gi\u00fap SLNA c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho t\u00e0i n\u0103ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1307","checkdouble":"191332"}]}